273
00:27:11,630 --> 00:27:13,371
Ahem. And, uh, three?

274
00:27:15,425 --> 00:27:17,917
That man is gonna change the world.

275
00:27:19,346 --> 00:27:22,009
With the emergence of the Soviet Superman,

276
