290
00:28:25,245 --> 00:28:26,907
Superior Man.

291
00:28:32,002 --> 00:28:35,746
Faster, stronger,
and far deadlier than our Russian friend.

292
00:28:35,839 --> 00:28:37,205
And once unleashed...

293
00:28:40,344 --> 00:28:46,215
